<tr><td class="navbox-abovebelow" colspan="3"><div>United Nations special rapporteurs bear mandates from the <a href="/wiki/United_Nations_Human_Rights_Council" title="United Nations Human Rights Council">United Nations Human Rights Council</a> and may hold the titles special rapporteur, independent expert or special representative of the Secretary-General, and are also referred to simply as mandate-holders.</div></td></tr>
